OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781287880
OL,3,CMajor delays as 'serious collision'
OL,4,Ccloses A66 in both directons
OL,6,FA stretch of the A66 has been closed
OL,7,Fin Cumbria following a "major
OL,8,Fincident" in the early hours of this
OL,9,Fmorning near Kirkby Thore.
OL,11,FPolice issued a statement at 5:20 am
OL,12,Fclosing the key route in both
OL,13,Fdirections between the A6 (Penrith)
OL,14,Fand the A685 (Brough).
OL,16,FNational Highways has stated that this
OL,17,Fhas resulted in long delays in the
OL,18,Fsurrounding area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
