OL,3,CMajor delays as 'serious collision'
OL,4,Ccloses A66 in both directons
OL,6,FThe organisation added: "We are
OL,7,Fworking closely with Cumbria Police
OL,8,Fand all emergency services involved in
OL,9,Fthe response to this incident to
OL,10,Fensure the road is opened as quickly
OL,11,Fand safely as possible."
OL,13,FCumbria Police says the A66 will
OL,14,Fremain closed for some time, drivers
OL,15,Fare currently being advised to follow
OL,16,Fdiversions.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
